import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { ITags } from '../tags.model'; @Component({ selector: 'jhi-tags-detail', templateUrl: './tags-detail.component.html', }) export class TagsDetailComponent implements OnInit { tags: ITags | null = null; constructor(protected activatedRoute: ActivatedRoute) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.activatedRoute.data.subscribe(({ tags }) => { this.tags = tags; }); } previousState(): void { window.history.back(); } }
